---
title: Grilled Beyond Meat® Burgers with Sweet Potatoes and Green Onion Mayo
description: The best of Mom's meatloaf and a Beyond Meat® burger on a toasted bun make up this delicious dish. Zesty green onion mayo is a great dipper for barbecued sweet potatoes.
